modules.description: Provides functions to serialize and deserialize records to and from CSV format using type annotations. Works with OCaml records and lists of strings representing CSV rows. Enables direct conversion between database query results and structured data types.

Provides a parser and generator for CSV data using a custom syntax extension. Works with OCaml types that can be serialized or deserialized into comma-separated values. Enables direct conversion between OCaml records and CSV files in a type-safe manner.
